    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剑斗模式</h2>当玩家遇到老怪，将会自动进入攻击模式或者防御模式。如果战斗难度更高，对战速度就会更快。攻击时，玩家向着敌方所防御的另一侧挥剑，防御时，玩家按照敌方攻击的方向作防御。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1491050/extras/b20ecdeb4a6d02be22b53c5fbe19ee8c.poster.avif?t=1655626425\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1491050/extras/b20ecdeb4a6d02be22b53c5fbe19ee8c.webm?t=1655626425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1491050/extras/b20ecdeb4a6d02be22b53c5fbe19ee8c.mp4?t=1655626425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小怪群体</h2>小怪群体基本以波浪式攻击，玩家可以透过挥剑，一下子打倒多数小怪。不过，同时要小心行动一致的敌方。如果玩家使用特殊攻击，闪避敌方攻击，一定能战胜。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1491050/extras/7587a731d2761ed43ff842e8fd2226b7.poster.avif?t=1655626425\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1491050/extras/7587a731d2761ed43ff842e8fd2226b7.webm?t=1655626425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1491050/extras/7587a731d2761ed43ff842e8fd2226b7.mp4?t=1655626425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小怪生成点</h2>小怪会出现的地点众多，当中包括大街、公园及屋顶，还有在一些大厦里面的任何楼层。为了找出敌人， 玩家可乘坐电梯，或者在大楼外墙上奔跑，亦可以从一个屋顶跳跃到另一个屋顶。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1491050/extras/89288269d2e916eb4b35d05afd85a8af.poster.avif?t=1655626425\" width=386 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1491050/extras/89288269d2e916eb4b35d05afd85a8af.w